<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>SkiResortBoot</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
	    <div class="navbar-inner">
	      <div class="container">
	        <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
	          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
	          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
	          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
	        </a>
			   <ul class="nav pull-right">
		            	<li><%= mail_to "skishopmanager@gmail.com", "Contact Us" %></li>
						<li><%= link_to "Already a customer? Sign in", new_store_session_path%></li>
			   </ul>
	        </div>
	      <ul class="nav secondary-nav">
            
          </ul>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	  </div>
	
	<div class="container">			
		<header class="jumbotron masthead">
			<div class="inner">
			<h1>Ski Shop Manager</h1>
			<p>Simple way to manage skis, boots and customers!</p>
			<p><%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_store_registration_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %></p>
			</div>
		</header>
		
		<div class="marketing">
		  <h1>Designed for you, by you!</h1>
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="span4">
		      <img class="bs-icon" src="assets/glyphicons_186_move.png">
		      <h2>Built with local input</h2>
		      <p>We consulted several specialists on the field, and taken their input into account. </p>
		    </div>
		    <div class="span4">
		      <img class="bs-icon" src="assets/glyphicons_340_globe.png">
		      <h2>Universal skills accessibility</h2>
		      <p>Simple interface making customer registration and management dead simple, you're just a few clicks away.</p>
		    </div>
		    <div class="span4">
		      <img class="bs-icon" src="assets/glyphicons_073_signal.png">
		      <h2>Always Up</h2>
		      <p>Online resources and access ensure your data is secure and protected. Regular backups make your information readily accessible from any device, anytime.</p>
		    </div>
		  </div><!--/row-->
		  <div class="row">
		    <div class="span4">
		      <img class="bs-icon" src="assets/glyphicons_039_notes.png">
		      <h2>Simple design</h2>
		      <p>You don't need over-engineered systems that are hard to understand and use, increase your customer turnaround speed with just a few clicks!</p>
		    </div>
		    <div class="span4">
		      <img class="bs-icon" src="assets/glyphicons_040_stats.png">
		      <h2>Reporting on your stock</h2>
		      <p>Manage your stock from your computer, see what's popular and track returns and cashflows.</p>
		    </div>
		    <div class="span4">
		      <img class="bs-icon" src="assets/glyphicons_057_history.png">
		      <h2>Time is money</h2>
		      <p>With the number of customers arriving at your resort, don't be limited by manpower, more customers should mean more rentals... for you!</p>
		    </div>
		  </div><!--/row-->
		

		</div>		
	</div>
	</body>	
</html>
